OL,3,CTrain passengers urged not to travel
OL,4,Con Sunday due to lack of staff
OL,6,FIt said in a statement that due to
OL,7,F"train crew being unavailable" it is
OL,8,Fadvising passengers "do not travel"
OL,9,Fbetween Manchester Victoria and
OL,10,FStalybridge, Manchester Victoria and
OL,11,FChester, Manchester Piccadilly and
OL,12,FChester, Manchester Piccadilly and
OL,13,FStoke, or Liverpool Lime Street and
OL,14,FBlackpool North.
OL,16,FThe operator added: "Services on some
OL,17,Froutes in and around the North West
OL,18,Fmay be subject to disruption and very
OL,19,Fshort notice cancellations.
