OL,3,CTrain passengers urged not to travel
OL,4,Con Sunday due to lack of staff
OL,6,F"We encourage everyone to plan ahead
OL,7,Fand check journeys before travelling,
OL,8,Fparticularly last trains of the day
OL,9,Fwhich may be earlier than usual and
OL,10,Fmay be cancelled at short notice.
OL,12,F"If you do travel, please leave
OL,13,Fyourself plenty of time to do so and
OL,14,Fdon't rely on last services."
OL,16,FThe operator has made a high number of
OL,17,Fcancellations in recent months,
OL,18,Fparticularly on Sundays.
