OL,3,CTrain passengers urged not to travel
OL,4,Con Sunday due to lack of staff
OL,6,FMany train drivers and other crew
OL,7,Fmembers do not have Sunday working
OL,8,Fincluded in their contracts, with
OL,9,Fnumerous operators such as Northern
OL,10,Foften relying on them volunteering to
OL,11,Fwork extra paid shifts to run
OL,12,Ftimetabled services on that day.
OL,14,FNorthern has been issued with a
OL,15,F"breach notice" by the Department for
OL,16,FTransport, which requires the operator
OL,17,Fto produce an improvement plan.
