OL,3,CTrain passengers urged not to travel
OL,4,Con Sunday due to lack of staff
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Northern said: "Our
OL,7,Fcustomers have experienced higher
OL,8,Flevels of cancellations in recent
OL,9,Fweeks and for that we are sorry.
OL,11,F"The underlying reason for services
OL,12,Fbeing cancelled remains traincrew
OL,13,Favailability and Sundays being
OL,14,Fcontractually outside of the working
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,F"The breach notice issued by the
OL,18,FDepartment for Transport is being
OL,19,Ftaken incredibly seriously and
OL,20,Fimproving the reliability of our
OL,21,Ftimetable remains our top priority."
